title: Ep. 147 S&A Investor - Why Oil Prices Will Never See $50
itunes:title: Why Oil Prices Will Never See $50
description: Jim Norman, editor of The Oil Card, tells us why oil prices will almost never fall below $50 - even though fundamentals suggest they should. Jim also gives us a history lesson on how the U.S. and Russia have been controlling the price of oil for decades.
